      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to find your absolute dream ride? You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty! It is in such pristine condition\u2014I have totally babied this car since the day I got it. It looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be head-over-heels. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
