    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2018 BMW M2 LCI, a pinnacle of the N55B30T0 longitudinal inline-six platform. This specimen features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission with engagement-driven rev-matching and the electronically controlled Active M Differential for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis integrity is factory-perfect, utilizing lightweight aluminum five-link rear architecture and forged 19-inch 437M wheels to minimize unsprung weight. Every surface reflects a life of climate-controlled storage; the Long Beach Blue metallic finish retains its original depth, and the interior carbon fiber trim remains free of UV degradation. This is a mechanically transparent, high-performance coupe with a documented service history and zero deviations from its original engineering specification.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
